01:17.277 --> 01:18.511
We gotta go, come on. Come on.

01:18.511 --> 01:19.712
Come on, come on, get up, get up.

01:19.712 --> 01:21.081
Just get up, just get -

01:21.081 --> 01:22.115
- [Woman] No!

01:25.919 --> 01:28.855
(arrow thuds)

