03:27.574 --> 03:29.008
- Hey, can you see me?

03:29.008 --> 03:31.578
- Yes, I can see you. Can you see me?

03:31.578 --> 03:33.913
- Yeah, I can see you. Yeah, it's working.

03:33.913 --> 03:35.248
- Yay.

03:35.248 --> 03:36.182
- Hi. - How are you?

03:36.182 --> 03:37.717
