04:11.751 --> 04:13.553
As long as it takes. (chuckles)

04:13.553 --> 04:15.455
Did you find the phlebotomy equipment, by the way?

04:15.455 --> 04:16.456
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

04:16.456 --> 04:17.290
I got it.

04:18.191 --> 04:19.892
