04:49.122 --> 04:51.824
- Okay. - Yeah, my boss needs me.

04:51.824 --> 04:53.426
- All right.

04:53.426 --> 04:54.661
See you soon.

04:54.661 --> 04:55.728
- Yeah.

04:55.728 --> 04:56.796
